scenes.description: Elizabeth and Raora are sitting on chairs, discussing playing a game for ice cream.
A mascot character, Sergeant Smokey (a scale), appears and orders the group into a boot-camp style training session.
A giant keyboard appears on the wall, and the group reacts with surprise and excitement.
The members take turns reading the rules for the first trial: 'Think Fast, Move Faster!'.
Smokey commands Cecilia to go first, and the group hypes her up as the challenge begins.
Cecilia's First Trial: She types the answers to various trivia questions on the giant keyboard while the others cheer.
The trial ends, and the group celebrates Cecilia's score of 9 points.
Smokey calls for the next challenger, and Elizabeth prepares to take her turn.
